reviewText: This is a very intense series and quite the emotional roller coaster. Compelling, dark and in some parts heart breaking. A must see.

Intriguing and captivating, the cast in this volume immediately grabs your attention from episode one. Definitely a much-watch in your a Skins fan. I was sorely disappointed after Volume 5, but this season definitely redeems itself. Entertaining and fun in the usual Skins fashion.

Season 6 is way better than Season 5!
Finally, this cast captivates and engages in a story that is worth seeing!
